\section{Nonlinear system example}

In this example system, there is a rod on a hinge (hinge at (x,y) = (0,0) ) with length $l$.
There is a spring, hinge-ly connected to the end of the rod, with the other end of the spring attached to a wall on the vertical axis at (x,y) = (0, $h_s_0$);

